5. Senna Hue Hotel
206 reviews
#5 Best Value of 727 places to stay in Hue
Luxurious hotel with spacious rooms, beautiful gardens, and top-notch spa. Ideal for families, offering private tours and easy check-in/out. Features executive suites, large pool, and exceptional massage services.
6. TTC Imperial Hotel
1,778 reviews
#6 Best Value of 727 places to stay in Hue
Elegant 5-star hotel near Perfume River, boasting stunning river views and harmonious East-West architecture. Spacious, well-appointed junior suites and corner rooms with modern amenities. Rooftop bar offers 360-degree city views and a temple on the 17th floor. Convenient location with friendly staff.
7. Azerai La Residence Hue
