Hotel near train station, riverside, restaurants, and landmarks. Spacious rooms, luxurious amenities including pool, spa, gym, and breakfast buffet. Professionally staffed and well-designed interiors.
9. Thanh Lich Royal Boutique Hotel
1,137 reviews
#9 Best Value of 727 places to stay in Hue
Elegant hotel boasting modern amenities, spacious rooms, luxurious bathrooms, and friendly staff. Offers pool, gym, spa, and exceptional breakfast buffet featuring Asian and Western options.
10. Indochine Palace
2,230 reviews
#10 Best Value of 727 places to stay in Hue
Well-maintained historic hotel in Hue offering clean rooms, comfortable beds, and excellent food. Ideally situated within walking distance to local bars and restaurants. Features a large swimming pool and impressive breakfast buffet. Known for friendly staff and luxurious ambience.
